                            <comment id="14471970" author="guillaume" created="Tue, 11 Oct 2011 06:30:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Another similar problem reported to me by Roshan, in Grails&apos; url mappings:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;name xxx: &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;/c/$authCode&quot;&lt;/span&gt;(controller: &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;foo&apos;&lt;/span&gt;, action: &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;bar&apos;&lt;/span&gt;) {
    constraints {
 &#160; &#160;    authCode blank: &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;
    }
}
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14471841" author="guillaume" created="Tue, 11 Oct 2011 06:33:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;And as a workaround for now, putting back the parentheses make things work:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;name(xxx: &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;/c/$authCode&quot;&lt;/span&gt;(controller: &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;foo&apos;&lt;/span&gt;, action: &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;bar&apos;&lt;/span&gt;)) {
    constraints {
        authCode blank: &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt; 
    }
}
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14471905" author="blackdrag" created="Tue, 18 Oct 2011 07:28:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;the reason for the bug was not because of a wrong or grammar rule, it was because of some semantic action executed only in certain cases, that was causing this. Took a while, but seems to be fixed now&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
